practitioner.about:
Dr. Orwa Bader is a Specialist in Internal Medicine at the Al Zahia branch of Medcare Medical Centre. After completing his MBBS from Tishreen University in Latakia, Syria he further qualified himself with a Syrian Board Specialization in Internal Medicine and one in Gastroenterology. He has also completed Part 1 of MRCP (Member of the Royal College of Physicians), UK and has a Master's degree in Internal Medicine. He is a member of the Syrian Syndicate of Physicians.

Dr. Bader commenced his career as an Internal Medicine Resident at the Tishreen University Hospital in Latakia gaining valuable experience through rotation in wards, ER and the ICU. He then joined the mobile clinic of the Syrian Arab Red Crescent as an Internal Medicine Specialist. He also served as an Internal Medicine Specialist at the Tabiat Hospital in Latakia attached to the ER and ICU Departments before returning to work with the Syrian Arab Red Crescent, followed by a stint with the Poly Care Medical in Freetown, Sierra Leone, West Africa. Subsequently, he relocated to the UAE.

Having garnered varied experiences in his chosen field, Dr. Bader is skilled at treating all types of acute and chronic diseases, respiratory infections, infectious diseases, dyspepsia, gastroenterology diseases, heart disease, kidney disease, neurological diseases, auto-immune diseases, brain diseases, thyroid diseases, influenza and endemic diseases. He has successfully treated patients with conditions like asthma, COPD, pneumonia, dysphagia, Crohn’s disease, ulcerative colitis, enteritis, hypertension, heart failure, arrhythmias, kidney stones, nephritis, headaches, seizures, viral hepatitis and diabetes. He treats anaemia, different blood diseases and vitamin deficiencies too.

He likes to dabble in art in his spare time, especially drawing. He speaks Arabic and English.

locations.about: Medcare Medical Centre in Al Zahia stands as a premium, advanced healthcare facility devoted to meeting the diverse healthcare needs of its community. This inviting medical centre prioritizes comfort and convenience, providing cuttingedge facilities and comprehensive medical services all under one roof. Ideal for patients of every age seeking precise diagnoses and prompt treatment across various specialties. At the helm of Medcare Medical Centre Al Zahia is a team of multicultural, multilingual doctors, complemented by exceptionally-trained and experienced nurses and medical staff. The centre takes pride in its extensive array of stateof-the-art equipment, empowering its highly skilled medical team to deliver a premium level of care to all patients. Experience the warmth of family-centric care delivered by our highly talented medical and non-medical staff. At Medcare Medical Centre Al Zahia, we offer a range of services, including Internal Medicine, Gynaecology, Paediatrics, Dermatology & Aesthetics, ENT, Dentistry, Orthopaedics and Physiotherapy. As part of our commitment to accessible healthcare, Medcare operates a network of four hospitals and 20 plus multi-specialty clinics across Dubai and Sharjah. Our goal is to provide reliable and timely medical care to our diverse clientele. Great News! We are expending to better suit all your medical and beauty needs!
